{"lastModified":1775211918372,"uri":"c::7819307041::vessel::d5cca393-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nVALIUM 55 is a luxurious 55 ft. catamaran built by Lagoon. A model created by passionate designers for sea lovers searching for freedom. VALIUM 55 features 5 cabins and accommodates 10 guests. A vessel with nothing left to chance, Lagoon has designed it in al its smallest details. You can enjoy a gentle lifestyle on board of VALIUM 55, far from the constraints of daily life.","blueprint":{"name":"VALIUM 55","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca393-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::1852f9b1-1ab1-11f0-9e81-09983e5c335e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca393-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::1852ab90-1ab1-11f0-9e80-09983e5c335e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca393-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::18519a20-1ab1-11f0-9e80-09983e5c335e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca393-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::18523660-1ab1-11f0-9e80-09983e5c335e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca393-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::1850fde0-1ab1-11f0-9e80-09983e5c335e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca393-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::184d5461-1ab1-11f0-9e80-09983e5c335e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca393-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::18528480-1ab1-11f0-9e81-09983e5c335e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca393-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::1852f9b0-1ab1-11f0-9e81-09983e5c335e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca393-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::18593b40-1ab1-11f0-9e82-09983e5c335e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca393-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::184df0a0-1ab1-11f0-9e80-09983e5c335e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca393-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::184f7